#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Continue inputting notes until you have filled the whole pre-selected region "
"(between the blue markers). <application>Qtractor</application> will let you "
"continue beyond that point, so you need to keep an eye on the marker "
"yourself."
