#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To scroll sideways, you can hold down either Shift or Ctrl and use your "
"mouse's scroll wheel."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Move to transport just before the end of the segment you added: use Shift-"
"click."
