#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the first MIDI segment to select it, then copy it by clicking on "
"'Edit &gt; Copy' or Control-c"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid "Paste it by clicking on 'Edit &gt; Paste' or Control-v"
